{"id": 477, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些想太多？", "description": "不怕一万，就怕万一，机会总是留给有准备的我的。", "record_count": 5132, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161852TzWluXMoEq8ndxRH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-14T13:50:20Z", "options": [{"id": 8193, "content": "喜欢过我的人有女朋友了，万一他还喜欢我怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160559}, {"id": 8705, "content": "梦想是要有的，万一遇到鬼了呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166510}, {"id": 8197, "content": "放假我要好好复习，然后开始想象考了清华北大要怎么装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107047}, {"id": 14341, "content": "我会变成有钱人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137889}, {"id": 8198, "content": "万一我一直在做梦都没醒过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161296}, {"id": 14598, "content": "我一定可以反杀( ⁼̴̀ .̫ ⁼̴́ )✧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120843}, {"id": 8199, "content": "万一下一秒我死了怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142481}, {"id": 9479, "content": "万一……好久不见的老朋友见面挺尴尬的…结果说的停不下来?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170605}, {"id": 8200, "content": "考的我都会，不会全蒙对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121172}, {"id": 18440, "content": "我觉得人喜欢我，又觉得人不喜欢我，再觉得人讨厌我，又觉得人离不开我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 8201, "content": "说不定校花在暗恋我呢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159551}, {"id": 8715, "content": "出门是迈左脚还是右脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166668}, {"id": 7948, "content": "— 万一我有小孩，就要这样教育 — 你有男朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 8204, "content": "我想娶个校花，不知道是不是想多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161350}, {"id": 8460, "content": "高考失利后直接选择打工会不会漂泊一生？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164091}, {"id": 7949, "content": "万一我今天买股票，明天跌了...万一我今天卖股票，明天涨了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121509}, {"id": 7950, "content": "没准我喜欢的人也正好在喜欢我呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 884, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138774}, {"id": 8206, "content": "万一真的有万一呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161381}, {"id": 7951, "content": "万一我死了，不我真的死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 7952, "content": "要好好修饰外表，万一我今天出门遇到女朋友了呢……", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127655}, {"id": 7953, "content": "别人是不是不喜欢我？是不是得向别人展现下自己让她认可我？（很多时候是你赞美他们，他们就喜欢你哈哈哈。）", "image": null, "praise_count": 282, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157611}, {"id": 8210, "content": "发这个会不会火了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161506}, {"id": 7955, "content": "万一我中奖了，该交多少税啊？（开始了计算）", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113378}, {"id": 7956, "content": "她提分手，是不是还爱我？", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158734}, {"id": 7957, "content": "万一我今天买彩票，明天发现中了五百万呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 432, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126996}, {"id": 8213, "content": "我走在路上，又多少人在看我？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161580}, {"id": 7958, "content": "放心～老师看不到的～", "image": null, "praise_count": 219, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153105}, {"id": 8726, "content": "她不理我可能只是因为忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154908}, {"id": 7959, "content": "万一中了六合彩，我在几环买厕所好？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 8215, "content": "穿越了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161625}, {"id": 7960, "content": "辞职创业，失败了咋办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60140}, {"id": 8216, "content": "万一地球爆炸了我们去哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160939}, {"id": 7961, "content": "男友还在和前女友联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153786}, {"id": 8218, "content": "假如我身高增加了。会不会比现在更帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161703}, {"id": 7963, "content": "他不理我，可能只是因为忙。", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 8219, "content": "万一我有超能力会是什么比较好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161726}, {"id": 8220, "content": "万一我减肥成功了呢…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161775}, {"id": 7965, "content": "万一，桃花太旺怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159083}, {"id": 8221, "content": "明天要早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157616}, {"id": 8477, "content": "老是幻想男朋友各种浪漫各种惊喜各种霸道而我各种小鸟依人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164268}, {"id": 8222, "content": "朋友都抱孩子了，我还没有女朋友，是不是该去相亲了？相亲是不是很老土？遇见喜欢的要怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161792}, {"id": 8478, "content": "我就进去一下下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164285}, {"id": 7969, "content": "万一别人跟着我买这场球，赚得还比我多怎么办？（还是一起上天台吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 7970, "content": "你只是怕伤害我。不是骗我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 8226, "content": "这次应该不会挂科吧_(:з」∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89674}, {"id": 8482, "content": "下一秒睁开眼发现我一直在做梦，恐惧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164305}, {"id": 7971, "content": "一个假期回到学校，马甲线练出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157101}, {"id": 7972, "content": "他不理我，可能是因为在忙吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154908}, {"id": 7973, "content": "万一有天发生了生化入侵，我会变异成什么样？", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159774}, {"id": 7974, "content": "做不出门的实验，就可以每天在家赖床看美剧了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}]}